OL,3,CPublic toilets under threat in
OL,4,CEastbourne as council tries to save
OL,5,Cmoney
OL,7,FEastbourne Council says it is facing
OL,8,Fexceptional financial challenges due
OL,9,Fto the high costs of homelessness and
OL,10,Ftemporary accommodation and has to
OL,11,Fmake an extra #2.7 million in savings
OL,12,Fthis year.
OL,14,FLast year, public toilets in
OL,15,FEastbourne cost more than #300,000.
OL,17,FThe community toilet scheme would mean
OL,18,Fbusinesses could offer their
OL,19,Ffacilities for public use or run some
OL,20,Fof the council's current public
OL,21,Ftoilets.
