OL,3,CPublic toilets under threat in
OL,4,CEastbourne as council tries to save
OL,5,Cmoney
OL,7,FThe council has committed to keeping
OL,8,Fone public toilet open on the seafront
OL,9,Fat the bandstand. Campaigners say the
OL,10,Ffour other seafront toilets could now
OL,11,Fclose.
OL,13,FThe consultation closes at 5pm on
OL,14,FThursday 31 October 2024.
